Package com.github.shiftac.upartier.network

Interface PacketVersion

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    PacketType, PacketType

    public interface PacketVersion
    PacketVersion interface defines the way we translate data from network into byte array that can be later read() by ByteArrayIO objects. To fully implement the protocol, user may later implement PacketType interface to define the way we explain the raw bytes(which class should we use to call read()?)
